node.accessibility_caption:
It’s Sunday! Let’s keep the fun going with some morning brunch shows at 11am and then 2pm- We are also ready to have some delicious rooftop drinks with this weather!!

Let’s not forget tonight’s t dance at 6pm and evening shows from 7-1130pm! 
We have an energized Sunday ready for you!

node.text:
Jumping into this weekend with the same energy @the_famous_frankk gives us on his spontaneous twerk lessons!! 
Join us for our brunch shows at 11am and 2pm- let’s grab a drink at our rooftop for a refresher,
Enjoy some sunset beats by @djlatrice and our evening shows from 7-1130pm!! 
We have a fun filled Saturday ready for you!!

node.accessibility_caption:
A magical Miami sunset with amazing music by the talented @djlatrice starting at 6pm! 
Let’s keep the weekend going 💃🏽💃🏽 at palace south beach

It’s Sunday and we’re not ready to stop the fun!
Lets keep it going with our brunch shows at 11am and 2pm, our amazing rooftop for drinks, we have our t dance at 6pm AND our evening shows from 7-1130pm!! 

We have a fun filled day and we hope you’re ready! 🙌🏽💃🏽💥🔥
